To build and install lgmon:

        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            ip4700
            mp250
            mp270
            mp490
            mp550
            mp560
            mp640

Example for building the mp640 lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=mp640
        make
        make install

